// original code working!!!

function Router()

   local cRoute := "home"

   if GetContent() != "home"
      if GetContent() == "login"
         cRoute = "login"
      else
         if GetAction() == "edit"
            cRoute = "edit"
         elseif GetAction() == "exec"
            cRoute = "exec"
         else
            cRoute = "browse"
         endif
      endif
   endif

return View( cRoute )

****************************************************************************


function Router()

   local cRoute := "home"
   local IScan := 0

   if GetContentViewFileName() != "home"
      if GetContentViewFileName() == "login"
         cRoute = "login"
      else

         IScan := AScan( aMenu_entries, { |a| a[ 2 ] == GetAction() } )

         if IScan > 0
            cRoute := aMenu_entries[ IScan, 3 ]
         else
            cRoute = "browse"
         endif


      endif
   endif
   logging( cRoute + "          Router" )

return View( cRoute )

//----------------------------------------------------------------------------//
